5.5.29" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.4.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 4, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.4.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 4, 64</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.69" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.101" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 101</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.1.57" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 1, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.1.94" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 1, 94</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 1, 48</bibl>.
<lb />Misapplied for <emph>approach</emph> by Launcelot: <bibl n="shak. mv 2.5.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 5, 20</bibl>.
